Fix pgaudit compilation with PostgreSQL 19beta1.

In PG19, VARSIZE_ANY_EXHDR changed its signature to accept (const void *)
instead of a raw Datum. Use DatumGetPointer() to properly convert.

diff --git a/pgaudit.c b/pgaudit.c
--- a/pgaudit.c
+++ b/pgaudit.c
@@ -835,7 +835,7 @@
 
                 if (auditLogParameterMaxSize > 0 &&
                     typeIsVarLena &&
-                    VARSIZE_ANY_EXHDR(prm->value) > auditLogParameterMaxSize)
+                    VARSIZE_ANY_EXHDR(DatumGetPointer(prm->value)) > auditLogParameterMaxSize)
                 {
                     append_valid_csv(&paramStrResult,
                                      "<long param suppressed>");
